{"title":"走人民公社的路","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走人民公社的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好比一只船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好比一只船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风鼓起船上帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舵手是咱毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶船的人六万万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北抚宁县董为璧）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天就把长江跨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自打有了高级社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙地起了大变化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今参加大公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天就把长江跨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北怀来县陈秉忠）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社属人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社属人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民当家作主人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员团结似兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡乡社社一家人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（上海曙光社张泽民）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农业一齐搞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社就是好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工业农业一齐搞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里庄稼比牛壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂烟囱比天高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河北怀来东风公社乔福钰）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵不缺少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵不缺少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社内有大队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产建设保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行动军事化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（陕西大荔县扈世德）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图纸已经设计好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破砖烂瓦全拆掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸碎锅台做肥料；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾把柴火烧新砖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐把楼房来建造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图纸已经设计好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东南西北林荫道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社四周流小河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河上面横大桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥上汽车似流星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员乘着满处跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又去工厂又下地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还去公园绕三绕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（顾工）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社有四多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产资金积累多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相协作人力多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大力革新农具多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统一领导经验多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都是活诸葛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（上海曙光社　张泽民）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社发电厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青砖墙，红瓦房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟囱竖到蓝天上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门口挂上白漆牌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“人民公社发电厂”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发电厂，真漂亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚来电机突突响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全社电灯一齐亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似星群落地上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏淮阴县  沈彦）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千条树枝一股根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千条树枝一股根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝连枝儿绿荫荫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万只手一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心齐黄土变成金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同走社会主义幸福春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（官厅人民公社  罗士钢）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔照片剪贴　左一摄制〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}